// --- Used to create a basic account of the waves at current
//      INPUT:
//          numWaves =      number of natural waves in the game, use GET_NUM_TIME_WAVES
//      CREATES:
//          A               no use beyond simple for loops
//          waves =         bitmask of all waves at current
//          WaveCount =     number of waves at current
// 
